OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FOne student has died from meningitis,
OL,7,Fand two others are being treated for
OL,8,Fthe disease following a small outbreak
OL,9,Fin southeast England.
OL,11,FThe small cluster of cases comes two
OL,12,Fmonths after a fatal outbreak in Kent
OL,13,Fin March.
OL,15,FThe UKHSA has confirmed that these
OL,16,Fcases are of a different strain to
OL,17,Fthat which caused the recent outbreak
OL,18,Fin Kent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
