OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778883107
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FThe outbreak of menB in Kent earlier
OL,7,Fthis year led to the deaths of two
OL,8,Fpeople.
OL,10,FAs a result, thousands of people were
OL,11,Fgiven the menB vaccine or antibiotics
OL,12,Fin a bid to curb the spread.
OL,14,FClose contacts of all three Reading
OL,15,Fcases have been offered antibiotics as
OL,16,Fa precaution.
OL,18,FHere is what you need to know about
OL,19,Fmeningitis, including symptoms, risks
OL,20,Fand how to protect yourself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
